{"tid":1925071,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真求救]覺得同男友淡左 點解決","createTime":"2020-03-14T06:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T16:41:46.000Z","uid":13395,"like":14,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"af2e3308a5d98c8bacfc379a2fa7b57577cae217","tid":1925071,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"第一次拍拖,同男朋友聽日就踏入第3個月,<br />\n由第2個月開始,其實已經覺得淡淡地,<br />\n雖然我地見面唔少,見面既時候都好sweet好癡纏,<br />\n但係愈黎愈悶,出街行街又唔知去邊,<br />\n唔係就番屋企扑野,話題愈黎愈少,好悶,<br />\n我同男朋友既價值觀唔同,<br />\n我講自己既睇法,佢唔同意就會鬧我唔成熟,幼稚,<br />\n同佢傾唔到計,我對佢既感覺越黎越淡<br />\n但我仲好鍾意佢 靠新鮮感唔知可以維持幾耐<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友好易亂諗,我唔敢同佢講,<br />\n怕講左佢會以為我唔鍾意佢,<br />\n同埋佢有抑鬱症,之前同我講過想自殺,<br />\n我好怕講錯野令佢唔開心或者做傻事"},{"pid":"24b73390ad04045fb5287e43de26c788f1e8f1c0","tid":1925071,"uid":11256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"點解要咁在乎情愛下"},{"pid":"086a6458289201980ccbaa833c35681477c8eae0","tid":1925071,"uid":11256,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"國難當前 仲談情愛"},{"pid":"231059d6cff9fefef55fd4769e14d4084308006f","tid":1925071,"uid":144056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"24b73390ad04045fb5287e43de26c788f1e8f1c0","tid":1925071,"uid":11256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"點解要咁在乎情愛下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:16:51.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"9562f8135ec5a4c4dd9a06dc336fb8889838457e","tid":1925071,"uid":144056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"086a6458289201980ccbaa833c35681477c8eae0","tid":1925071,"uid":11256,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"國難當前 仲談情愛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:17:01.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"4eb9f50373300775193d75d3741d33d99cf3b94b","tid":1925071,"uid":2936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"你同男友點識的"},{"pid":"16adfaeb10875af65fc70e16774f3624